item.title: THM_Kenobi_Walkthrough
item.description: Kenobi THM performed by: jb-willams Deploy the vulnerable machine Scan the machine with nmap, how many ports are open? Deploy the Machine and scan it with nmap nmap -v -p- -sV -sC -T4 -oA nmap/initial 10.10.223.56 && grep -i "open" nmap/initial.nmap | cut -d' ' -f 1 | cut -d'/' -f1 | tee nmap/ports.txt | wc -l notice, you may get some false positives that will have unknown service, ignore them
